{"tid":2252153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自己一個係咪真係仲開心","createTime":"2020-10-21T09:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T10:31:24.000Z","uid":367476,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"357bc484d5bef1ad257b1a3f80988fd8a5593a57","tid":2252153,"uid":367476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:39:47.000Z","msg":"有時覺得自己一個比拍拖仲開心 自己一個可以咩都唔洗理 咩都可以做 唔洗比人管住你有咩做得有咩唔做得 而家亦多咗啲時間可以做自己嘢 唔洗嘥時間同佢去邊同佢傾計<br />\n<br />\n我而家喺甩咗難啦亦覺得時間真係多咗係開心咗 但我真係好唔捨得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住同佢過嘅日子同埋好掛住同佢傾計嘅回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好矛盾"},{"pid":"6630666bb8dfb23c768c6d152e59dccb792c6940","tid":2252153,"uid":230905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6771b42fc033574375cd5e3168e85cc3fe38f4d3","tid":2252153,"uid":86375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:46:11.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住, 已經個半月, 我仲係日日都諗住佢"},{"pid":"467b3fb9b18422b3e3b13d1bb7a10e8a66ee9b06","tid":2252153,"uid":19215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:09:52.000Z","msg":"係 唔好諗啦"},{"pid":"77e5a2c92f5c888136b4da68d843453186b33704","tid":2252153,"uid":318074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"成日都係咁 單身想拍拖 拍拖想單身"},{"pid":"690d6b205754b558fd1b2592092af0b84079d569","tid":2252153,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"一個寂寞一個煩，冇話邊個好嘅<br />\n<br />\n不過拍拖可以隨時分手，但你未必可以隨時拍長拖"},{"pid":"9d1edf465a5043cbcb712a7bed8f7cec4d84430d","tid":2252153,"uid":378624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"以為自己出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas